7
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:25,160
And so in an interview, this is a very popular question.

8
00:00:25,339 --> 00:00:26,800
Why did you leave your last job?

9
00:00:27,140 --> 00:00:29,960
Learn some tools for answering this question in today's dialogue.

10
